description:
1800 Reposado (meaning rested in Spanish) is double distilled for smoother, cleaner flavor and aged in French and American oak barrels.

Directions
Enjoy a shot of 1800 Reposado using our iconic bottle stopper as a shot glass. 1. Place stopper halfway in the mouth of the bottle enough to seal the opening. 2. Invert the bottle to allow tequila to fill stopper. 3. Turn the bottle horizontally to remove shot-filled top. 4. Enjoy your 1800 shot.
